304
00:13:10,498 --> 00:13:12,875
<i>Seo-yoon, you've got this.</i>

305
00:13:12,958 --> 00:13:16,337
JEON SEO-YOON
FANGIRLING HER WAY INTO REAL LIFE DATING

306
