345
00:15:15,456 --> 00:15:20,544
<i>Hello. I'm Yoon Jung-yun,</i>
<i>a 26-year-old eternal single.</i>

346
00:15:21,503 --> 00:15:24,131
WHY ARE YOU AN ETERNAL SINGLE?

347
00:15:24,214 --> 00:15:26,050
First of all,

348
