364
00:16:10,594 --> 00:16:12,888
He never makes eye contact, right?

365
00:16:12,972 --> 00:16:13,973
<i>You're right.</i>

366
00:16:14,056 --> 00:16:15,265
MOCK BLIND DATE

367
00:16:19,561 --> 00:16:22,272
<i>This is my very first blind date.</i>

368
00:16:25,234 --> 00:16:27,111
