369
00:16:27,194 --> 00:16:28,779
<i>My hands got so clammy.</i>

370
00:16:31,156 --> 00:16:32,241
<i>I was so nervous.</i>

371
00:16:33,325 --> 00:16:34,827
Hello.

372
00:16:35,327 --> 00:16:36,620
Oh, gosh.

373
00:16:36,704 --> 00:16:38,414
