-Hello.

374
00:16:40,082 --> 00:16:42,501
-Nice to meet you.
-Likewise.

375
00:16:55,514 --> 00:16:56,557
<i>He can't even look at her.</i>

376
00:16:57,474 --> 00:16:59,560
<i>-He can't make eye contact at all.</i>
<i>-He can't talk either.</i>

377
