382
00:17:25,794 --> 00:17:30,382
<i>I have no trouble hanging out</i>
<i>and having fun with close friends.</i>

383
00:17:32,843 --> 00:17:35,971
<i>But I get so awkward around women.</i>

384
00:17:36,055 --> 00:17:38,891
<i>I stutter a lot and stuff like that.</i>

385
00:17:40,309 --> 00:17:42,644
-During our conversation,
-Okay.

386
00:17:42,728 --> 00:17:44,938
